1 AN ACT concerning
2 Condominiums – Property Insurance Deductibles – Unit Owner Responsibility
3 FOR the purpose of increasing the maximum amount of the council of unit owners’ property
4 insurance deductible for which a unit owner is responsible under certain
5 circumstances; providing that a contract for the resale of a condominium unit by a
6 unit owner other than the developer is not enforceable unless it contains a written
7 notice of the unit owner’s responsibility for the amount of the deductible where
8 damage or destruction originates from a unit; and generally relating to condominium
9 unit owners’ responsibility for the council of unit owners’ insurance deductibles.
